+# Image Thumbnail Resizer
+
+A small Flask app for uploading an image, resizing it to a target width, previewing the generated thumbnail, and downloading the result.
+
+## Run locally
+
+```bash
+python -m venv .venv
+.venv\Scripts\activate
+pip install -r requirements.txt
+python app.py
+```
+
+Open http://127.0.0.1:5011 in your browser.
